                     <hi rend="largeCaps">ALFRED BEAUMONT</hi> (31)</persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18690503-483-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18690503-483-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
